    "description": "Kaizen Platform, Inc., provides user experience (UX) solutions to improve conversion rates (CVR) for client websites. The company operates in two segments, Growth and Transformation. The Growth segment offers services such as, website production, customer relationship management (CRM) improvement, and video production, primarily under performance-based quasi-entrustment contracts. The Transformation segment provides consulting services for corporate digital transformation (DX), including DX workshops and system engineering services, mainly under performance-proportion quasi-commission contracts. It offers KAIZEN AD/VIDEO, which enhances advertising and mass production resources; KAIZEN CONSULTING, which supports DX project launch, strategy planning, and administrative support; KAIZEN SCHOOL, a video advertising creator training course; KAIZEN ENGINE, which improves customer experience across systems; and KAIZEN AI CLOUD, which manages various generative AI APIs and middleware. The company was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Minato, Japan."
